                  </persName>
            . I cannot swear to the prisoner.</p>
               <p>BROWN EDWARDS. I am an officer. On the 15th of April I searched the prisoner's bedstead in the pantry at Mr. Gordon's and in a drawer under it, found the duplicates of this property.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 22.</p>
               <p>Of <rs id="t18240916-180-verdict981" type="verdictDescription">
